  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3540645/" class="title-link">入门手册，但感觉还是蛮专业的。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3540645"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/hero0419/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u44697329-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/hero0419/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">无重力</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-13"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-13 14:51:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3540645_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本书大篇幅的抄袭了陆子峰的《GO!GO!GO!》第三分册 —— 狙击战术技巧手册，同时翻译了美军战地狙击训练手册《FM 23-10 Sniper Training》的部分内容，这两本书的质量是不错的，本书的质量自然很好。  WarGame爱好者或者军事爱好者，备上一本这样的书是很有必要。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
