  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3481686">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3481686/" class="title-link">作为了解狙击手和狙击战的入门读物还可以</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3481686"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/44025790/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u44025790-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/44025790/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">散兵</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-07-28"
      class="main-meta">2010-07-28 13:17:22</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3481686_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  国内的确是没有啥比这本书更系统全面地了解狙击手和狙击战的了，为此推荐之。 但如果要更深度些，建议直接浏览外文网站，即便维基（英文）上的东西也比这本书更深入，别说有些老外狙击手的个人网站了...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3481686_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3481686_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



